Recommends: ffmpeg, fuse-ts, fuse-vdv
Description: Client for interacting with the CRS Tracker and helper libraries
 CRS::Tracker::Client is a library for interacting with the CRS Tracker via XML-RPC with
 automatic encoding of all arguments.
 CRS::Executor is a library for execution of XML jobfiles generated by the CRS Tracker.
 CRS::Fuse is a set of libraries to interact with fuse-ts and fuse-vdv.
 CRS::Auphonic is a library to use the web services of auphonic.com.
